headline: Conagra Brands to Unveil New Innovations and Discuss Updated 2025 Outlook at CAGNY Conference
summary: Conagra Brands, Inc. (NYSE: CAG) announced that its upcoming presentation at the annual Consumer Analyst Group of New York (CAGNY) Conference will detail Conagra's advantaged market position, perspective on the evolving consumer environment, and unique focus on the science of growth. Conagra will also preview a series of new innovations expected to launch in calendar year 2025 and provide detail on its updated fiscal 2025 financial guidance.
